{"article_id":"yRdc6QxRph9weM8A","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Alabama has become the latest US state","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"to move to restrict abortions","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"by passing a bill","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to outlaw the procedure in almost all cases .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"The law includes a ban on abortion in cases of rape or incest .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Supporters say","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"they expect the law to be blocked in court","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"but hope","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that the appeals process will bring it before the Supreme Court .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"They want the court ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"which now has a conservative majority ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"to overturn the 1973 ruling","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"legalising abortion .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Alabama 's 35-seat Senate is dominated by men ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"and none of its four female senators backed the ban .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"It was then signed by Alabama 's Republican governor , Kay Ivey .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Sixteen other states are seeking to impose new restrictions on abortion .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Earlier this year the Supreme Court blocked implementation of new abortion restrictions in Louisiana .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"However the ruling was made by a narrow margin","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and the case is due to be reviewed later this year .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The bill 's architects expect","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that it will be defeated in the lower courts ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"but hope","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that it will therefore eventually come before the Supreme Court .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"They have been emboldened by the addition of two conservative justices","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"nominated by President Donald Trump , Neil Gorsuch and Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"who give the nine-member court a conservative majority .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Their aim ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"they say ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"is for the landmark 1973 Roe v Wade ruling to be undermined or overturned completely .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Alabama 's Lieutenant Governor Will Ainsworth said :","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"`` Roe must be challenged ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"and I am proud","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"that Alabama is leading the way . ''","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Eric Johnston ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"who founded the Alabama Pro-Life Coalition","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"that helped draft the bill ,","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"told NPR :","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"`` The dynamic has changed . `","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"` The judges have changed , a lot of changes over that time ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and so I think","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"we 're at the point","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"where we need to take a bigger and a bolder step . ''","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"Under the bill , doctors face 10 years in prison","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"for attempting to terminate a pregnancy","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"and 99 years","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"for carrying out the procedure .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"A woman","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"who has an abortion","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"would not be held criminally liable ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and abortion in cases","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"where the mother 's life is at serious risk","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"are allowed .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"The state Senate approved the law by 25 votes to six ,","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"rejecting exemptions for cases of rape or incest ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"with some noting","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"all those voting for the bill","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"were men .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Democrats here in Alabama knew","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"they had no chance","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"of stopping this controversial bill ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"but that only seemed to make the debate on the senate floor even more heated .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Activists packed the senate gallery","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"to watch the drama play out -","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"reacting with laughter and gasps in turn .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"The few women","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"who spoke on the floor","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"were quick to highlight a key fact :","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"this decision about women 's bodies was being made almost entirely by men .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"As one female lawmaker introduced a sure-to-fail amendment to the bill","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"to make it illegal for men to get vasectomies ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"the gallery and overflow watch room upstairs burst into laughter .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"On the senate floor ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"when the amendment failed ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"the lawmaker made her point ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"saying :","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"We have never policed men 's bodies the way","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"we do women 's .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Just outside the stark white walls of the state legislature were still more pro-choice advocates ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"raising signs","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that called for women 's equality ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"for protecting Planned Parenthood ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"for men to stay out of women 's rights issues .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"One exasperated young woman told me :","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"`` We 've already had this vote about women before .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"In the 70s .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Why are we here again now ? ''","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Earlier this year the governors of four states","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"- Georgia , Kentucky , Mississippi and Ohio -","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"signed bills","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"banning abortion","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"if an embryonic heartbeat can be detected .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Opponents say","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"this amounts to a ban on abortion","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"because cardiac activity in an embryo can be detected as early as the sixth week ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"before a woman may be aware","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that she is pregnant .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"The Guttmacher Institute ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"which campaigns for reproductive rights ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"says","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"none of these bans are yet in effect ,","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"but their introduction is part of the same strategy","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"to get the cases heard by the Supreme Court ,","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"it says .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"Overall 28 states are currently considering legislation","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"that would ban abortion in a variety of ways ,","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"it says .","depth":4},{"id":107,"text":"Dr Yashica Robinson ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"who is one of the few doctors","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"left providing abortion in Alabama ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"told BBC Radio Four 's PM programme","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"that she would continue to do her job","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"while fighting for women 's access to abortion in the state .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"`` I will still be here","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"taking care of women","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"and doing the things","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"I can legally do , ''","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"`` Then , I will be helping women to the places","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"they need to be","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"in order to get the healthcare","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"that they desire or need","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"if they are going to make it difficult here . ''","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"Alabama Democratic state Senator Bobby Singleton said","depth":4},{"id":124,"text":"the bill `` criminalises doctors ''","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"and was an attempt by men `` to tell women what to do with their bodies '' .","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"Several Democratic presidential hopefuls also reacted on social media ,","depth":5},{"id":127,"text":"including Kamala Harris .","depth":5},{"id":128,"text":"The National Organization for Women called the ban `` unconstitutional ''","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"it was `` a transparent effort","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"to drum up political support for anti-abortion candidates in upcoming elections '' .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Staci Fox of Planned Parenthood Southeast Advocates called the decision `` a dark day for women in Alabama and across this country '' .","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"In a statement she said","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"Alabama politicians would `` forever live in infamy for this vote","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"and we will make sure","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"that every woman knows who to hold accountable '' .","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"There are currently three abortion clinics in Alabama , down from more than 20 in the 1990s ,","depth":5},{"id":138,"text":"according to pro-choice campaigners .","depth":5},{"id":139,"text":"Other states have seen similar falls in the number of abortion clinics","depth":6},{"id":140,"text":"and in 2017 , six states reportedly had just one abortion clinic in operation .","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"However states with liberal majorities are seeking safeguards to the right to abortion in their own constitutions .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":248,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"N